{"tid":2178063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳光誠撐特 籲各國阻華侵略","createTime":"2020-08-28T06:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T06:52:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"257529ce73ff06a7d4061893e9e11778fc278c4c","tid":2178063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:50:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200828/7WERYH7GBBAYRCL3MERJWMSKWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200828%2F7WERYH7GBBAYRCL3MERJWMSKWM%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=a1e026be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200828%2F7WERYH7GBBAYRCL3MERJWMSKWM%2F&h=120acfac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200828/7WERYH7GBBAYRCL3MERJWMSKWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n陳光誠撐特 籲各國阻華侵略<br />\n<br />\n在奧巴馬政府年代逃到美國定居的中國失明維權律師陳光誠，前日出席共和黨全國黨代表大會演講，讚揚總統特朗普有對抗中國的勇氣，呼籲其他國家支持特朗普帶頭組成聯盟，「阻止中國侵略」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：指拜登當選 美將推行社會主義  騷亂下接受提名 彭斯撐警打治安牌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rsZxsJUta1hWrHxR8pn-TN60eQ0=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JCC63Z2JDFA4LAGGK7RET2OUDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrsZxsJUta1hWrHxR8pn-TN60eQ0%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJCC63Z2JDFA4LAGGK7RET2OUDM.jpg&h=34a0a839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳光誠讚揚特朗普敢於對抗中國。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讚特朗普有鬥爭勇氣<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。「中共是人性的敵人，恐嚇自己的人民、威脅世界的美好。美國必須運用其自由、民主和法治的價值，跟其他民主政權組織聯盟阻止中國侵略。特朗普總統已帶頭行事，我們需要其他國家加入，為未來作戰。」<br />\n<br />\n陳光誠揭露中國一孩政策下地方官員強迫民眾墮胎後，成為了國際人權代表。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：七槍射癱黑人 威州警身份曝光<br />\n<br />\n當時陳光誠在醫院病房接受美聯社訪問時，說美方官員告訴他，如果他繼續逗。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社"},{"pid":"f8573903920b31797d7a89ae786d4160cf23a316","tid":2178063,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b899ddee4ac2668c0ddb96a455914b5c3e9302d","tid":2178063,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"Good"}]}